@startuml
title Please use '!option handwritten true' to enable handwritten

actor SuperUser
participant Browser
participant Server
database Database

SuperUser ->> Browser : navigate to profile
Browser->Server: loadAllUsers()
activate Server
Server->Database: fetch
return 
deactivate Server
Browser<-Browser: display 

note over SuperUser,Browser #DDF0FF#FFFFFF[<b><font color=black>Please use <color:red>'!option handwritten true'</color>\nto enable handwritten</font></b>]


SuperUser ->> Browser :  enable/disable user  
Browser->Server: changeStatus(user)
activate Server
Server->Database: save
return 
deactivate Server
Browser <- Browser:display 


@enduml